    {
        "content": "<p>Suppose we have a non-zero analytic function on a connected set <code>U</code>. What are the possible values for <code>{x ‚àà U | f x ‚â† 0}</code>? I thought it was <a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=Filter.codiscreteWithin#doc\">docs#Filter.codiscreteWithin</a> of <code>U</code>, but this example shows that's wrong</p>",
